      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It sounds like you are in a place of profound despair, and the idea of stopping the struggle feels like the only relief available. Please understand that the desire to stop the pain is understandable, but there are people who want to help you find a different kind of peace. If you are feeling this way, please contact the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline right now at 988. They are there to listen without judgment and help you navigate these overwhelming feelings.",
