    "summary": "The user expresses profound despair and existential exhaustion following several academic and professional failures, eventually hinting at a desire to \"opt out\" of life. The assistant responds by acknowledging the user's pain and validating their feelings of being overwhelmed, while consistently providing crisis resources and suggesting professional help.",
